SELECT "t"."Id", "t"."RunningTimeInMinutes", "t"."Title", "t"."YearOfRelease", "r0"."Id", "r0"."MovieId", "r0"."UserId", "r0"."Value"
FROM (
    SELECT "m"."Id", "m"."RunningTimeInMinutes", "m"."Title", "m"."YearOfRelease", (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM("r"."Value"), 0)
        FROM "Ratings" AS "r"
        WHERE "m"."Id" = "r"."MovieId") AS "c"
    FROM "Movies" AS "m"
    ORDER BY (
        SELECT COALESCE(SUM("r"."Value"), 0)
        FROM "Ratings" AS "r"
        WHERE "m"."Id" = "r"."MovieId")
    LIMIT @__p_0
) AS "t"
LEFT JOIN "Ratings" AS "r0" ON "t"."Id" = "r0"."MovieId"
ORDER BY "t"."c", "t"."Id", "r0"."Id"

        SELECT COALESCE(SUM("r"."Value"), 0)
